**他們在4月21日成為第一支開季吞下6連敗卻拿下11連勝的球隊，最後他們將連勝紀錄推進到13場。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/a-s-walk-off-in-error-filled-10th-inning|title=11 straight for A's after unreal walk-off win|website=MLB.com|access-date=2021-05-01|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422154342/https://www.mlb.com/news/a-s-walk-off-in-error-filled-10th-inning|dead-url=no}}</ref>

