**他在5月21日登上大聯盟，成為大聯盟史上第兩萬名選手。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/mariners-catcher-jose-godoy-becomes-20000th-player-in-mlb-history/|title=Mariners catcher José Godoy becomes 20,000th player in MLB history|website=CBSSports.com|access-date=2021-07-04|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524123701/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/mariners-catcher-jose-godoy-becomes-20000th-player-in-mlb-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

