**他們在5月22日單場敲出2支滿貫砲，合計7支全壘打，為大聯盟紀錄。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/ronald-acuna-jr-hits-grand-slam-in-rout|title=Braves smash home runs, history books|website=MLB.com|access-date=2021-07-04|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605091050/https://www.mlb.com/news/ronald-acuna-jr-hits-grand-slam-in-rout|dead-url=no}}</ref>

